  <chapter role="api-reference">
      <title>Summary of Changes</title>
      <para>
          This extension adds capabilites to the RAX-KSGRP extension.
          It allows for CRUD operations on groups and gives the
          ability to assocate groups with users.
      </para>
      <section>
          <title>New Headers</title>
          <para>None.</para>
      </section>
      <section>
          <title>New Faults</title>
          <para>None.</para>
      </section>
      <section>
          <title>New Resources</title>
          <para>
              A new resource is created at /RAX-GRPADM/groups that
              allows for the management of groups.
          </para>
          <resources xmlns="http://wadl.dev.java.net/2009/02">
              <resource href="RAX-GRPADM.wadl#groups"/>
              <resource href="RAX-GRPADM.wadl#group"/>
